entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have gotten Entha enough skins from infected womp rats that the local health authorities will be able to develop a vaccine against this current strain of grunge fever.
entries.journal_entry_description: Entha Kandela is the Animal Control officer for Mos Eisley. She is severely under-funded.  The vermin population outside the city walls is becoming a major public health hazard. The first task that she has for you is to take a census of the areas of infestation around Mos Eisley.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: This is the fifth area to check for infestations.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Womp Rats and Mound Mites have been added for that location. Thank you.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: This is the fourth area to check for infestations.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Tempest Rills and Mound Mites have been added for that location. Thank you.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: This is the third area to check for infestations.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Tame Worrts and Rock Mites? Okay, they have been added to the census.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: This is the second area to check for infestations.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: Tame Worrts and Sickly Womp Rats? Okay, I have added this data to the census.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: This is the first area to check for infestations.
entries.task10_comm_message_text: Carrion kreetles and city sewer swamp rats? Okay, those are noted, thank you.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Entha has a number of reports of vermion infestations. You need to go to each one of them and do a census of the vermin population there.
entries.task13_comm_message_text: Great job. This is worse than I expected. Come on back and we can settle up.
entries.task14_journal_entry_description: Head back to town and speak with Entha.
